{
  "stem": "1917.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And because we had so much malnutrition problems, we needed to get the milk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I kept wondering how-- I worried, well, does this vampire know that I am Jewish, so he wouldn't attack me?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a child, I didn't question the fact that this was fabricated by somebody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was worried that he was going to attack me, that he wouldn't know that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, there were a lot of other problems, even though the slogans of the communist were brotherhood, equality.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they did-- they did do a very interesting things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put me and my sister in charge of the Youth Communist Party in our school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Here, all of a sudden, I was a big shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was deciding what young-- who is going to join the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would ask them questions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very active.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was very enthusiastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the first time in my life that anybody said that  I was equal to them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was always very independent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on a-- in 1948 in a May Day parade, I was leading of 30 pioneers, as well as my sister had with 30 pioneers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were supposed to go in the morning to a May Day parade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then lunch we had picnic in the park.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we had a torch parade in the evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the next day, we had school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And according quote to the Communist Party, children, the students, had to be the best communist-- had to be the best student in their class.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I just very simply said to my students, you have a test tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We are not going to the torch parade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You go home and study.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's more important to study.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
